title: American Mcgee's Grimm 1-5 (2009) (Digital) (Pirate-Empire)
description:
English | CBR | 5 Issues

American Mcgee's Grimm #1-5
Publisher:  IDW Publishing
Publication Date:  April 15, 2009 - September 23, 2009

Writer:  Dwight MacPherson
Artist:  Grant Bond
Letterer:  Neil Oyetake
Cover Artists:  Grant Bond and Ben Templesmith

Game designer American McGee's Grimm introduces the lovably macabre Grimm into famous fairy tales, transforming them into hellish nightmares. Now Grimm unleashes his dark magic on many comic book archetypes, twisting superhero tales, romance comics, westerns and more to his own purposes. Up first, Crisis On Earth 57, where Grimm launches a secret invasion crisis into a domain where villains are doomed to fail until he gets involved!

Thanks goes to Pirate for this release.
